Wen, Hu Say Addressing Southwest China’s Drought Top Priority

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-10T13:04:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-10/wen-hu-say-addressing-southwest-china-s-drought-top-priority.html
Chinese Premier  Wen Jiabao  and
President  Hu Jintao  have ordered relevant agencies to focus on
battling drought in areas of Southwest  China  where rainfall has
been below normal, according to a statement on the government’s
website today.  Wen and Hu also designated water sanitation as a top
priority to minimize the impact on residents, according to the
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kae Inoue at 
 kinoue@bloomberg.net  